metadata.name: Wrecks - Optical Jazz vol. 2
metadata.description:
“And how do we take up space.
And how of we fill these spaces, together.”

The focus is volume. How we enter a space, how we read and interact with the space and others in it.

Volume is defined as the space occupied within the boundaries of an object in three-dimensional space. It is also known as the capacity of the object.
